{"tid":2127665,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"11.2維園內吸煙遭截查 拒向便衣警出示身份證 退休漢罪成罰款2,000元","createTime":"2020-07-27T12:18:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T12:19:14.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a9b7611d3a2985a2f0df1c27ba813645e2bcdb6f","tid":2127665,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T12:18:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200727/UMW7KFDBAX2UXI5QUDLZZ7XD4U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200727%2FUMW7KFDBAX2UXI5QUDLZZ7XD4U%2F&d=ducsj56GsZITs%2BYA0ylwpWE7lpprR278wgWha8tNVfY%3D&h=d7a00c7a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200727%2FUMW7KFDBAX2UXI5QUDLZZ7XD4U%2F&h=16a231fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200727/UMW7KFDBAX2UXI5QUDLZZ7XD4U/</a><br />\n<br />\n六旬退休工程師去年11月於警察進入維園驅散民主派區議會選舉候選人集會期間，在園內吸煙兼沒依照便衣警要求出示身份證，因而被捕，及後遭控以未能在規定下出示身份證明文件等罪。暫委裁判官黃向戎今裁決指，涉案警員身穿防暴裝備，上面寫有「警察」等字樣，已能表露警務人員身份；加上被告當時稱呼警員為「阿sir」，又謂「拉囉」，均證明被告明知對方是警員，裁定被告罪成。連同早前已承認的在禁煙區內吸煙罪，被告共被罰款2,000元。"},{"pid":"bc1e2e10549927e3882229363c22091d798d5f1d","tid":2127665,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T12:19:14.000Z","msg":"簡單一封信，無窮愛意話你知<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2127624\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2127624</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}